Calculates the cuts to be applied to the T0, Charge and Timing variables
The function to call is 

    int optimizeCuts(...)

defined in optimizedCuts.C.
The full arguments list is

    int optimizeCuts(const char *fileNameIn, // name of the input root file
                     const string outputFolder, // name of the output folder (must exist already)
		     const string flag, // flag for the output plot names
		     const bool holdPlots = false){ // leaves the TCanvas open at the end of the script

Define flags that may be modified:
       #define T0CUTNSIGMA 3. // number of sigmas for T0 cut
       #define TIMINGCUTFRACTION 0.01 // fractional area for Timing cut